==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tricennial
<hw>Tri*cen"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tricennium</ets> thirty years; <ets>triginta</ets> thirty +
<ets>annus</ets> year: cf. L. <ets>tricennalis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to thirty years; consisting of thirty years; occurring once
in every thirty years.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tricentenary</ent>⟦br⟧
